          </p>
          <p class="helpIntro">
            Inspired by the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Checklist-Manifesto-How-Things-Right/dp/0312430000">Checklist Manifesto</a> by Atul Gawande, Eucalyptus was designed to be able to create, store, and manage tasks. We believe there is a direct correlation between simplicity and stability, and by implementing FlightPlans we can make these complex processes much simpler. By leveraging Eucalyptus, we increase consistency while providing education, logs, and enabling collaboration.
